message.body: Am I able to use your computer? I have to complete a module online for work and my computer has stopped working. Some drivers stopped working and now my screen is black but still running and I've done three hard shut downs and still nothing! I really ordered a new one at the right time.
Hey Eden. I'm sorry I had interviews and meetings all day. Do you still need it?
It's ok. I figured you were busy. I do still need it but I don't know if I feel like doing it now so it's ok.
Okay sorry. Let me know though I'll be there in an hour.
My mom's not cooking so there is left over gravy. Just a heads up in case you didn't want it again.
